{
  "stem": "6719.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That-- although speaking, and, if there was such I thing as dreaming-- I do not believe that I ever dreamt, but maybe I did-- speaking, we spoke and created the most fantastic dishes.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I remember an incident and that happened in, I think, in 1943, when a man, a prisoner, a haftling, an inmate, got killed because he couldn't stop talking about the food that he is going to create.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Somebody in the-- in the barracks killed him for it because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the worst thing-- not incident, but the worst thing-- was hunger.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nobody that doesn't know what real-- and I mean, when I say real hunger it means nothing-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] doesn't know how much that hurts.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Yeah, I wanted to kill them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I conjured during the day in my mind how I'm go about to kill Otto-- Otto [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Graf ?] or-- or Franz Wunsch or then after this incident when we were on the roof in crematorium five, what I would do with Otto Moll.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow it soothed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was very angry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I-- I know I'm jumping far ahead, but when I came out, I had only one priority, a priority.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had other things, but my priority was to find them and kill them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I literally, I say this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in some cases, I succeeded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm not sorry for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, you change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, priorities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- I'm not going to say you know what my-- my priorities are to talk to young people and tell them what it's all about.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This interview is not my prior-- it still isn't my priority.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
